{"tid":1417372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勿忘初心，爭取最多支持者為重任","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:08.000Z","uid":264983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90a94eef528ec8157ac5314baae4f32d9fd945c8","tid":1417372,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:27:35.000Z","msg":"手足，仲記得初心嗎？<br />\n我哋話不篤魁 不割蓆 不譴責<br />\n無論和理非 泛民 定中間派，<br />\n我哋堅持到而家。<br />\n<br />\n但係，仲有另一個初心，<br />\n不受傷 不流血 不被捕！<br />\n而家點呢？<br />\n<br />\n記住，<br />\n我哋要爭取嘅<br />\n係更多中間、甚至淺藍<br />\n轉向我哋，<br />\n可唔可以暫時唔好再衝、唔好再堵路、唔好不合作運動？<br />\n至少，唔好玩激烈，咪俾柒婆陰到啊！<br />\n（我指暫時，即係等儲下彈藥先）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為再繼續偏離初心，<br />\n民意會流失、人心會攰，<br />\n我哋就前功盡廢。<br />\n<br />\n而且，如果更多人被捕，<br />\n係再冇更多義務律師或社工幫手㗎！咁你哋到時點算？<br />\n再講，<br />\n明知黑警選擇性執法，<br />\n明知黑警亂射亂扑，<br />\n明知正苦指鹿為馬顛倒是非，<br />\n明知政權製造白色恐怖，<br />\n明知黑社會無法無天...<br />\n點解仲要俾晒機會人哋咁蠢？<br />\n<br />\n要冷靜喇！<br />\n近日除咗 Be Water 外，<br />\n仲講緊Be humble，<br />\n可以試試嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果大家真係好夠精力、想做啲嘢，<br />\n不如直接做啲爭取民心嘅事：<br />\n你哋唔洗乜券物券咪幫手派俾啲好有需要嘅人囉（做到老人家、新移民、少數族裔讚大家，正苦冇得玩分化）<br />\n你哋應該更有創意嘅，幫手諗多啲、share出去，同埋付諸行動啦！<br />\n<br />\n我信你哋真係做到完美㗎！"},{"pid":"b1483b0fad6e1435cedaac536fcc5f7dcaf82ae0","tid":1417372,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kp2a6SZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKp2a6SZ.png&h=1fca8dff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003004_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003004_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=6861e66b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003005_7ac1c5bed2d04486296b242c94e2c328.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003005_7ac1c5bed2d04486296b242c94e2c328.png&h=0f95e9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003006_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003006_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=3880c87a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003007_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003007_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png&h=8389467e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}